# Keyboard / focus

- **Guard** graph shortcuts (delete, copy, paste, dup, undo, redo) when an **input is focused** or **dialog/overlay** is open — early return (`isInputFocused || isDialogOpen`).
- **Spacebar:** ~**200 ms hold** → temporary pan/hand tool; release → prior tool; quick tap stays with existing bottom-bar play/pause behavior. Capture phase OK; still honor guards unless a dialog explicitly overrides.

**Ref:** `docs/user-goals/11-undo-redo-and-keyboard.md`.
